Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wish no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be okay if you came out to laugh at me and say, "You fledgling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd tell me to awkwardly struggle until the very end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am one of your loyal subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Reines?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bow my head down to Sir Sophia-Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to resolve a complicated situation over at Spiritual Evocation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:00.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:29.63,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My, oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it won't take too much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I do find you to be very charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time, Primary Lecturer Wills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to show you such a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You still are popular with the girls as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thinking though to leave the door open
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when you'll be alone with a female student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time we've spoken like this since your father's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got all personal affairs in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Trevor Pelham Codrington was a grand Necromancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I give you my condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to ask of me as one of the authorities in Spiritual Evocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, my father purchased wasteland,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,including a whole ancient Roman monument.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marbury Workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Transforming an entire wasteland into a Workshop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the strength of its magical energy rivals that of a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Marbury Workshop ran out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With a series of lightning falling, not only did all the family Magi perish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but more than a dozen local civilian lives were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last casualty was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was caused by a leyline becoming warped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For Magical Workshops of that style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to think of other sources of magical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's strange that someone as prolific as Sir Trevor couldn't repair it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If accidents at the Workshop continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing I can do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, elder brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if this continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the Marbury Workshop will be taken up by the main Codrington family, land and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But if a Workshop of that caliber is confiscated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it would hurt Bram, as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have one more thing I needed to consult you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about that on-site.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful you egged him on, Princess of El-Melloi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for the next department head\Nof Spiritual Evocation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,my elder brother vows to even pull chestnuts out of the fire as needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What beautiful sisterly love you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But is he still obsessed with that ritual?\NHoly Grail War, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Clock Tower is sending Atrum Galliasta
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and Bazett Fraga McRemitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But there still is a slot left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what my elder brother believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to mediate, I could probably shove him into the McRemitz slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think someone who is at least temporarily a Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to bow down to me for a shady ritual like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now. The previous Lord El-Melloi and your little sister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,both died in a shady Holy Grail War, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I should mourn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you shrivel up without any curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you finally talk to me about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is essentially within Spiritual Evocation's jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The main Codrington family filed a complaint about this to the Policies Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To Policies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that the Workshop is unstable because of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and at this rate, it will breach Concealment of the Mystics,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so the main family needs to manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be troublesome for that guy Bram.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Spiritual Evocation openly meddling in an inheritance dispute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would give them a bad rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I was the one set to doing Sir Sophia-Ri a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do anything it takes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if it means I can participate in a Holy Grail War once again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Reines?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to endure it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the leyline balance is less stable than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She has Mystic Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. When Reines comes in contact with magical energy, her eyes turn red.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not often that pain accompanies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like back when I was younger when I stuck my hand into the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I'll be okay as long as I use some eye drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be better for us to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind elements are moving furiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't think we'd be walking such a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a frail little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is a little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have finally returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd already be over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Adashino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Lord El-Melloi II.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as a complaint has been filed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the duty of Policies to promptly carry out an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result of that investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wills Pelham Codrington is under arrest as a suspect in the murder of Sir Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on just a minute!\NHow did things end up that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you father-killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Waletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Adashino, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She is Waletta Codrington,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,sent from the main Codrington family of Necromancy to ascertain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon arrival,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I immediately tried calling down\NSir Trevor to learn his circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But all traces of him were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's quite the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling someone down with Necromancy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is summoning the residual thoughts of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, not all who have died can be called down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The residual thoughts can wear down, or the communication can be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Erasing all traces of him is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. To erase all traces of residual thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is similar to someone wiping away fingerprints in a criminal investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can only be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,by a Necromancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. That is only circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are ignoring the possibility of other perpetrators.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking just Sir Trevor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to call down everyone involved in these accidents involving lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time lightning has fallen, Wills was present within the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding, Waletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I tried to call down the soul of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And can you prove that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe all of this evidence will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you saying a great detective is entering the scene again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In this storm, it's dangerous to drive a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you haven't forgotten how Sir Trevor passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, at the least, we're riveted here until this storm passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, Miss Adashino,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like permission to investigate this Workshop until the storm passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Modern Magecraft Theory dares trample upon Spiritual Evocation matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, the Spiritual Evocation\NDepartment requested this of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll share what we find with both Policies and the main Codrington family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hishiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he can't escape anyway, it's useless to restrict him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You haven't been cleared of your suspicion yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not you're the perpetrator will come into light with the investigation, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't pass judgement on anything that has yet to be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the way of a scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my father's study.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you related to that young lady Waletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a childhood friend from the main family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened, and she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you refuse to marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! What a brilliant detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sentenced by Policies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll likely take over this Workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a transparent picture to paint sounds like something she'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you? How are you related to Miss Adashino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the worst compatibility in all of the Clock Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, can you finally talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about the other reason why you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems she is here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a Fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be a Fairy rooted to this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She started to appear around when the Workshop was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That day was also stormy like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see Fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairy Eyes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that strong for Mystic Eyes,\Nbut I was born with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time she gives me a warning, someone dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what she is warning me against.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wild Hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,An order of Fairy knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Reines, it's not good to investigate the mansion without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this magical energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A hidden corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting into the swing of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't! We need to inform Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we do that, Adashino will catch on, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to investigate this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's my principle to voluntarily do things others don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell because I'm a grave-keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, these are ruins a Necromancer purchased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the main keep for the Magical Workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon for the eye drops to lose effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. These ruins are creating a response from my Mystic Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These ruins are drawing out the power of my Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, missies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These are spirits who were guarding the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they perceive you missies as grave robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not wrong per se.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting even more excited now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a secret passageway back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be slightly rough for an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you missies can keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Reines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shishigou Kairi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Necromancer and a mercenary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally from Japan,\Nhe accepts even the dirtiest of jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite famous over at Policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall I still had a seat in the Clock Tower for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is a celebrity like him here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shishigou is one of my father's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to express my condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And? You didn't even show up at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was a visitor doing in the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That graveyard is connected to the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more convenient to pass through there to avoid lightning in getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wills, kiddo, is the room I usually use still left as is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, why are we in the same room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's optimal for bearing children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch... Wh-Why such a thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, your magic circuits are complete garbage of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not a bad seed for a successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad idea to use this opportunity to set it up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! You still can't take a joke, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have that much energy, I guess you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The underground graveyard was a hive of spirits, but this bed is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The leyline of this land reacts with Mystic Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder, Mystic Eyes, graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I need just a little more for everything to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what Gray says and be a good girl by staying in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Hishiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Modern Magecraft Theory intervening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to hand this Workshop over to the likes of Bram!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For us Magi, the howdunit and the whodunit are both meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all of that can be decided for by all of us in Policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the warped image the correct one or is it mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what we determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:47.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:17.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Waletta was struck by lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have yet another casualty?
